<main class="min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">
        {gettext("Pricing")}
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-base-content opacity-70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        {gettext(
          "Stride is free to self-host on day one. Pay us only if you want it managed for you."
        )}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-base-300 p-8 flex flex-col">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-base-content opacity-60 mb-2">
            {gettext("Solo")}
          </h2>
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-2">
            <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-base-content">{gettext("Free")}</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70">
            {gettext("Self-host. Forever. No card required.")}
          </p>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Unlimited boards, tasks, goals")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Bring any agent — Claude, Cursor, Aider, Codex, your own")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Full agent API + client-side hooks")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Single user")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Community support on GitHub")}</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <.link
          href={~p"/users/register"}
          class="block w-full text-center px-5 py-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-base-300 text-base-content font-semibold hover:bg-base-200 transition-colors"
        >
          {gettext("Get started")}
        </.link>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border-2 border-primary p-8 flex flex-col relative">
        <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-primary text-primary-content text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide">
          {gettext("Most popular")}
        </span>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-base-content opacity-60 mb-2">
            {gettext("Team")}
          </h2>
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-2">
            <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-base-content">{gettext("$12")}</span>
            <span class="text-base-content opacity-70">{gettext("/ user / month")}</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70">
            {gettext("Hosted by us. For teams that don't want to run a server.")}
          </p>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Everything in Solo, plus:")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Up to 25 users on one workspace")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Goal-driven assignment + per-user agent fleets")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Daily backups, encrypted at rest")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Email support, 1-business-day response")}</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <.link
          href={~p"/users/register"}
          class="block w-full text-center px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-primary text-primary-content font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
        >
          {gettext("Start free trial")}
        </.link>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-base-300 p-8 flex flex-col">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-base-content opacity-60 mb-2">
            {gettext("Enterprise")}
          </h2>
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-2">
            <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-base-content">{gettext("Custom")}</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70">
            {gettext("Self-host or hosted. Whatever your security team needs.")}
          </p>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Everything in Team, plus:")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Unlimited users")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("SSO (SAML / OIDC) and SCIM provisioning")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Audit log export, custom retention policies")}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-base-content opacity-80">
            <.icon name="hero-check" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <span>{gettext("Dedicated success manager + custom SLA")}</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a
          href="mailto:enterprise@stridelikeaboss.com"
          class="block w-full text-center px-5 py-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-base-300 text-base-content font-semibold hover:bg-base-200 transition-colors"
        >
          {gettext("Talk to us")}
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-base-content mb-6 text-center">
        {gettext("Frequently asked questions")}
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 p-5 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-base-content">
            {gettext("Is Stride really free if I self-host?")}
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
            {gettext(
              "Yes. The whole codebase is open source under the MIT license. Run it on your own machine, your own server, or your own Kubernetes cluster. You owe us nothing."
            )}
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 p-5 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-base-content">
            {gettext("What counts as a user on the Team plan?")}
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
            {gettext(
              "Any human with a login. Agents — Claude, Cursor, Aider, Codex, your own — are not billable. They authenticate via API tokens scoped to a board and a user, and there is no per-agent fee."
            )}
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 p-5 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-base-content">
            {gettext("Can I switch between self-hosted and hosted later?")}
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
            {gettext(
              "Yes — both ways. The data model is the same. Export your workspace from one and import it into the other."
            )}
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 p-5 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-base-content">
            {gettext("Do you offer a discount for non-profits or open-source projects?")}
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
            {gettext("Yes. Email ")}<a
              href="mailto:hello@stridelikeaboss.com"
              class="text-[var(--ink)] hover:text-[var(--stride-orange)] underline font-medium"
            >hello@stridelikeaboss.com</a>{gettext(
              " with a short note about your project and we will set you up."
            )}
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
